        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">
          The rewards of Sadaqah extend far beyond this world, encompassing spiritual, physical, and communal blessings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Purifies Wealth -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
