          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">Sadaqah cleanses your wealth and removes greed from the heart, replacing it with gratitude and contentment.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Shade on Day of Judgment -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Shade on the Day of Judgment</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">The believer's charity will serve as shade and protection on the Day of Resurrection when there is no other shade.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Cure for Illness -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Cure for Illness</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">The Prophet (peace be upon him) advised treating the sick with Sadaqah. It is a means of seeking healing through generosity.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Protection from Calamity -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Protection from Calamity</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">Sadaqah acts as a shield against trials and tribulations, warding off misfortune and difficulty by the permission of Allah.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Increases Sustenance -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Increases Sustenance</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">Wealth given in Sadaqah does not decrease. Allah replaces what is spent and increases provision for the generous giver.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Extinguishes Sin -->
        <div class="sq-benefit-card bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.657 18.657A8 8 0 016.343 7.343S7 9 9 10c0-2 .5-5 2.986-7C14 5 16.09 5.777 17.656 7.343A7.975 7.975 0 0120 13a7.975 7.975 0 01-2.343 5.657z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.879 16.121A3 3 0 1012.015 11L11 14H9c0 .768.293 1.536.879 2.121z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">Extinguishes Sin</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">Just as water puts out fire, Sadaqah extinguishes sins and mistakes, purifying the soul and drawing one closer to Allah.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== 9. HADITH QUOTE 3 ===== -->
  <div class="my-12 mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
    <div class="bg-[#f8faf9] border-l-4 border-[#01534d] rounded-r-xl p-8">
      <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#01534d]/30 mb-3" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path d="M14.017 21v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.995 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.983zm-14.017 0v-7.391c0-5.704 3.731-9.57 8.983-10.609l.998 2.151c-2.432.917-3.995 3.638-3.995 5.849h4v10h-9.986z"/>
      </svg>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed mb-4" style="font-family: Georgia, serif;">
        "The believer's shade on the Day of Resurrection will be his charity."
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#01534d] font-semibold">
        -- Hadith (Ahmad/Musnad)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ===== 10. HOW YOUR SADAQAH IS USED ===== -->
  <section class="py-12 sm:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3" style="font-family: 'Signika', sans-serif;">
          How Your Sadaqah is Used
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;">
          Your generosity directly funds life-changing programs across the globe.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        {impactCards.map((card: any) => (
          <div class="sq-impact-card bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto bg-[#01534d]/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
              {card.icon === 'food' && (
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8.25v-1.5m0 1.5c-1.355 0-2.697.056-4.024.166C6.845 8.51 6 9.473 6 10.608v2.513m6-4.87c1.355 0 2.697.055 4.024.165C17.155 8.51 18 9.473 18 10.608v2.513m-3-4.87v-1.5m-6 1.5v-1.5m12 9.75l-1.5.75a3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 00-3 0 3.354 3.354 0 01-3 0L3 16.5m15-3.38a48.474 48.474 0 00-6-.37c-2.032 0-4.034.126-6 .37m12 0c.39.049.777.102 1.163.16 1.07.16 1.837 1.094 1.837 2.175v5.17c0 .62-.504 1.124-1.125 1.124H4.125A1.125 1.125 0 013 20.625v-5.17c0-1.08.768-2.014 1.837-2.174A47.78 47.78 0 016 13.12M12.265 3.11a.375.375 0 11-.53 0L12 2.845l.265.265zm-3 0a.375.375 0 11-.53 0L9 2.845l.265.265zm6 0a.375.375 0 11-.53 0L15 2.845l.265.265z"/>
                </svg>
              )}
              {card.icon === 'water' && (
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#01534d]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418"/>
                </svg>
